reviews.review_text: ME-80’s !! part deux ok … I jumped the gun a bit (shotgun ..lol) .. after a full listen, while the instrumental reproduction still amazes me, the mids are a tad lacking.. and it reveals in the vocals … still caught off guard by the sound, but after a little research, a condenser style does have shortcomings .. either way I stand by my initial thoughts … great reproduction of what we heard in that arena this night … keep ‘em comin’ !!
